quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,Haa Miim
  44,2,Ndahiriye ku gitabo (Qur’an) gisobanutse
  44,3,"Mu by’ukuri, twakimanuye mu ijoro ryuje imigisha (Laylat-ul Qadri). Rwose turi ababurizi (b’uko ibihano bizashyikira abahakanyi)"
  44,4,"Muri iryo (joro) ni bwo buri kintu (kizaba mu mwaka) kigenwa (amafunguro, igihe cy’amavuko, igihe cyo gupfa, amakuba)"
  44,5,"Ni iteka riduturutseho. Mu by’ukuri, ni twe twohereza (intumwa)"
  44,6,"Ku bw’impuhwe ziturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe. Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ni Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  44,7,Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo; niba muri abizera b’ukuri (nimube ariwe musenga wenyine)
  44,8,Nta yindi mana iriho itari we (Allah). Ni we utanga ubuzima n’urupfu. Ni Nyagasani wanyu akaba ari na we Nyagasani w’abakurambere banyu
  44,9,Nyamara bo bari mu gushidikanya bikinira
  44,10,Ngaho tegereza umunsi ikirere kizazana umwotsi ugaragara
  44,11,Uzapfukirana abantu. Icyo ni igihano kibabaza
  44,12,"(Bazavuga bati) \"Nyagasani wacu! Dukize ibihano! Mu by’ukuri, turaba abemera"
  44,13,"Ni gute bakwibuka kwemera (ubu), kandi bari baragezweho n’intumwa (Muhamadi) ibasobanurira"
  44,14,"Maze bakayitera umugongo, bakavuga bati \"Uyu ni umuntu wigishijwe (n’abandi) kandi ni umusazi"
  44,15,"Rwose turabakuriraho ibihano mu gihe gito, kandi nta kabuza muzongera musubire (mu buhakanyi)"
  44,16,"Umunsi tuzabahanisha igihano gikomeye. Mu by’ukuri, tuzabaryoza (ibyo bakoze)"
  44,17,"Kandi mbere yabo (ababangikanyamana) twagerageje abantu ba Farawo, ubwo intumwa yubahitse (Musa) yabageragaho"
  44,18,"(Irababwira iti) \"Nimumpe abagaragu ba Allah (mbajyane). Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi intumwa yizewe iboherejwemo"
  44,19,Ntimukanishyire hejuru imbere ya Allah. Rwose mbazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara
  44,20,"Kandi nikinze kuri Nyagasani wanjye ari na we Nyagasani wanyu, kugira ngo mutantera amabuye"
  44,21,Ariko nimutananyemera mundeke (ntimungirire nabi)
  44,22,"(Nuko bashaka kumugirira nabi) maze atakambira Nyagasani we agira ati \"Mu by’ukuri, aba bantu ni abagizi ba nabi (ubandinde)"
  44,23,"(Allah aramubwira ati) \"Ujyane n’abagaragu banjye nijoro; rwose (Farawo n’ingabo ze) baraza kubakurikira"
  44,24,"(Nimumara kwambuka) ureke inyanja igume uko iri ituje. Mu by’ukuri, (Farawo n’ingabo ze) baraza kurohama"
  44,25,(Ese Farawo n’abantu be) basize ubusitani n’imigezi bingana iki
  44,26,Ibihingwa n’amazu meza
  44,27,Naho umudendezo babagamo banezerewe
  44,28,Uko ni ko byagenze! (Imitungo yabo) twayizunguje abandi bantu
  44,29,Ikirere n’isi ntibyigeze bibaririra123 kandi ntibigeze bakererezwa (guhanwa)